node.title: Person found dead inside house on fire in Avondale
node.description: A person has died after a house fire in the central Auckland suburb of Avondale overnight.
node.content:
["A person has died after a house fire in the central Auckland suburb of Avondale overnight.", "", "
(File image) Photo: RNZ / Claire Eastham-Farrelly
", "Emergency services were called to the fire on Blockhouse Bay Road just after midnight.", "One person was found dead inside the house and neighbouring residents were evacuated as a precaution.", "Police said they were working with Fire and Emergency investigators to determine the cause of the fire."]
